{"tid":994342,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"專業player入","createTime":"2019-01-24T15:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T15:39:47.000Z","uid":46480,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c5bdf5f881332c8331c4d046b5ccb1beeb6fc3","tid":994342,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"識左個好多人追既靚女，有家底，白滑長腿，大波瘦底，但係個價值觀完全唔得，成日話想見識下上流社會既生活，好高騖遠，而且我發現佢有可能係比人包養緊（佢唔知我搵到啲hints)<br />\n但係佢又不斷約我單獨去玩去旅行，我reject左佢都keep住約（唔係兵，9成9係AA, 有時直頭係佢請）<br />\n如何做一個專業player地玩盡佢而唔沉船？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fe8103e4c18d48e29036cd93e3d570db5237d0","tid":994342,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"只要你用一個玩玩下既心態 其實唔難"},{"pid":"75c9024e1a46f4e2dd2b5b389a2c2af8a9e236b4","tid":994342,"uid":209225,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"你留你tg<br />\n我會令你感受屌到你射嘅滋味<br />\n利申 185 大隻型男"},{"pid":"8560c8b748c94f84e062fc02e406bd5ff49c5fa4","tid":994342,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74fe8103e4c18d48e29036cd93e3d570db5237d0","tid":994342,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"只要你用一個玩玩下既心態 其實唔難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"佢都好撚識玩，喺我發現佢係雞之前我都差啲沉咗船，依家及時抽身"},{"pid":"20bd4f46e7b343a1be121094f37d9e476aea4776","tid":994342,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8560c8b748c94f84e062fc02e406bd5ff49c5fa4","tid":994342,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74fe8103e4c18d48e29036cd93e3d570db5237d0","tid":994342,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"只要你用一個玩玩下既心態 其實唔難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"佢都好撚識玩，喺我發現佢係雞之前我都差啲沉咗船，依家及時抽身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"咁大家都知咩事啦咁咪同佢去旅行啦"},{"pid":"126788c5724371c257f0a